OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMainly dry
OL,6,Fwith the best of the brightness across
OL,7,FOrkney this evening. Cloudier skies in
OL,8,FShetland, perhaps some patchy light
OL,9,Frain. Moderate west or southwest winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FAny early brightness will
OL,12,Ffade with outbreaks of rain developing
OL,13,Fduring the day, perhaps turning heavy
OL,14,Fand thundery later. Light to moderate
OL,15,Fsoutheast to southwest winds.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FEarly
OL,18,Frain on Friday, becoming dry and
OL,19,Fbright. Occasional rain or showers on
OL,20,FSaturday and Sunday. Variable winds,
OL,21,Ffresh at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
